        // If $n$ is odd, we can assign $a_0, \dots, a_{n-1}$ to class 1 and $a_n, \dots, a_{2n-1}$ to class 2.
        // Both classes have $n$ students (odd).
        // Median of class 1: $a_{(n-1)/2}$.
        // Median of class 2: $a_{n + (n-1)/2}$.
