        // Since $k_1+k_2 = n-1$, $k_2 = n-1-k_1$.
        // $M_2 - M_1 \ge a_{2n-1-(n-1-k_1)} - a_{k_1} = a_{2n-1-n+1+k_1} - a_{k_1} = a_{n+k_1} - a_{k_1}$.
